headline.print_headline: Former Calpers Board Member Charged With Bribery in Corruption Case
headline.main: Former Calpers Board Member Charged With Bribery in Corruption Case

lead_paragraph: A federal grand jury indicted on Thursday a former Calpers board member on charges of bribing a chief executive of the California public pension fund and faking documents to gain million of dollars in investments fees.
